  "title": "MECHANICAL DRAUGHTSMAN",
  "description": "<ul><li>Create 3D designs for internal mechanical projects.</li><li>Provide technical support during equipment downtime.</li><li>Preparation and checking of fabrication drawings, to meet quality requirement, production capability and delivery schedule</li><li>Work closely with engineers, and project managers to ensure drawings meet project needs and standards</li><li>Conduct quality checks on drawings to ensure accuracy and completeness before submission.</li><li>Update drawings and layouts to reflect changes and improvements.</li><li>Friendly personality, Positive attitude and Team player</li><li>Good communication skills</li><li>Problem-solving skills.</li><li>Dedicated with desire to strive towards excellence</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p>How to Apply:<br />By submitting any application or resume to us, you will be deemed to have agreed and consented to us collecting, using, retaining and disclosing your personal information to prospective employer for their consideration.<br /><br />We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified. Wish you all the best.<br /><br />Damian Tan Wee Boon (EA Reg No: R1102628)<br />Active Manpower Resources Pte Ltd (EA Lic No: 06C3757)</p>",
